data.description: NEW ROOF COMPLETED JANUARY 2024- SHINGLE & FLAT  - PRICE REDUCED $$ - Impeccably maintained 2 bedroom 2 bath 1 car garage - double wide circular driveway - roofed screened pool & patio - 8,500 sq ft waterfront canal lot with a seawall - tastefully remodeled kitchen and baths - tile flooring diagonal layout - accordion storm shutters - "no carpet" all Cooper City "A" rated schools - no HOA - automatic sprinkler system - newer interior 6 panel doors with lever handles - freshly painted.  Truly move-in condition. Community Amenities: Beyond schools, Cooper City offers a wealth of amenities, including parks, sports facilities, enhancing your family's quality of life. Call today for your private showing.
